  title `Repeal and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_21_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_21_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_3_20_00080_A2023-49_1704690560714&sectionId=81361&sectionno=21&orderno=21&orgactid=AC_CEN_3_20_00080_A2023-49_1704690560714
obj_root_law_sections_21_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Election Commission (Conditions of Service of Election`
  line `Commissioners and Transaction of Business) Act, 1991 (11 of 1991) is hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Anything done or any action taken or purported to have been done or taken under the Act hereby`
  line `repealed shall, insofar as it is not inconsistent with the provisions of this Act, be deemed to have been done`
  line `or taken under the corresponding provisions of this Act.`
  line
  line `(3) The mention of particular matters in sub-section (2) shall not be held to prejudice or affect the`
  line `general application of section 6 of the General Clauses Act, 1897 (10 of 1897) with regard to the effect of`
  line repeal.
obj_root_law_sections_21_footnotes:
